{"tid":1252473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抛磚] 2020垃圾會, 我地需要幾多議席?","createTime":"2019-06-23T04:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T12:25:46.000Z","uid":66324,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"53688f244a4c578b67de45d755eb6c8b6a9cb62b","tid":1252473,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"想控制垃圾會, 有三個層次:<br />\n<br />\n1. 三分之二 (47) --- 完全控制立法會 (*由於保皇黨唔會誇張到連10席地區都無, 所以合拼埋兩邊過半)<br />\n2. 兩邊過半 (18 + 18) --- 可以推倒政府議案, 同埋可以令自己議員的議案可以通過<br />\n3. 純粹過半 (36) --- 可以推倒政府議案<br />\n<br />\n假如2020直選議席分佈不變, 而且非保皇有紀律(只出以下的數字+1), 而又無人出黎鳩雷, 唔駛我計大家估到非保皇可以拎到幾多席:<br />\n港島: 3/6<br />\n九西: 3/6<br />\n九東: 3/5<br />\n新西: 5/9<br />\n新東: 5/9<br />\n總數: 19/35<br />\n<br />\n有無可能拎多D? 如果選民成份變化不大, 個人認爲九西有機, 新東就要睇保皇會唔會又甩轆<br />\n如果今次可以成功令得票壓到上 7:3 新西同港島都應該可以順利拎到<br />\n假設<span style=\"color: red;\">21/35</span>先<br />\n<br />\n即係話而家我地要:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 三分之二 (47) --- 26 (Mission Impossible)<br />\n2. 兩邊過半 (18 + 18) --- 18 (全部功能組別)<br />\n3. 純粹過半 (36) --- 15</span><br />\n<br />\n而功能組別入面, 而家非建制控制的有9席:<br />\n教育界, 法律界, 會計界, 醫學界, 衛生服務界, 社會福利界, 區議會（第二） *3<br />\n相信呢9席2020果陣都穩陣, 所以而家要拎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 三分之二 (47) --- 17/26 (Mission Impossible)<br />\n2. 兩邊過半 (18 + 18) --- 9/26 (全部功能組別)<br />\n3. 純粹過半 (36) --- 6/26</span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地只需要拎到7席 (如果醫學界係中間派) 就可以拉死政府的政策<br />\n個人覺得有potential的有以下界別<br />\n1. 工程界<br />\n2. 建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界<br />\n3. 飲食界<br />\n4. 勞工界 (三席) &lt;--- 注意呢個界別係all or nothing<br />\n5. 批發及零售界<br />\n6. 進出口界<br />\n7. 區議會(第一) &lt;--- 如果可以控制到DC呢席自動獲得, 所以DC係重要<br />\n<br />\n9up完交比各位聰明的連登仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228e64a2dc46a2cf5ca3cdafd991c86df7287763","tid":1252473,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e05a7c5c04e1f0e089a7bccfdca425e0de952621","tid":1252473,"uid":103230,"like":7,"dislike":26,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"而家唔適宜講選舉"},{"pid":"2667fb975e26d29b9ea75ff21f35aece884fbd38","tid":1252473,"uid":66324,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"e05a7c5c04e1f0e089a7bccfdca425e0de952621","tid":1252473,"uid":103230,"like":7,"dislike":26,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"而家唔適宜講選舉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"無乜時間, 要及早plan定"},{"pid":"01cee83e854adc606ab7f1319c765ed3ae832703","tid":1252473,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2667fb975e26d29b9ea75ff21f35aece884fbd38","tid":1252473,"uid":66324,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"e05a7c5c04e1f0e089a7bccfdca425e0de952621","tid":1252473,"uid":103230,"like":7,"dislike":26,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"而家唔適宜講選舉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"無乜時間, 要及早plan定"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"唔爭在過埋呢個月<br />\n<br />\n你唔見連泛民都避開唔提？"},{"pid":"c3b19f373c00e5773da0ccc61e73d6048f3cbc97","tid":1252473,"uid":37081,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"都係果句<br />\n泛民肯讓路先算<br />\n一到選舉咩人性都出哂黎"},{"pid":"591e89bb1f2b728fb06887db3e4bf2e52c08651b","tid":1252473,"uid":39777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"最好係兩邊過半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但邊有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191e15b668dda351d096dcf7549df3fa75a6bef0","tid":1252473,"uid":66324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"01cee83e854adc606ab7f1319c765ed3ae832703","tid":1252473,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":